data.description: A short distance to area amenities, this home feels miles from the grind. Perfectly updated with a neutral color palette that flows throughout, this 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home has also been updated with a new gas boiler, newly installed hot water baseboards, updated electrical, and windows.  The roof is approximately 3 years young.  The newly tiled kitchen boasts updated custom cabinetry, upgraded counters, backsplash and new appliances.  All 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom are situated on the second floor.  Come visit this home at the open house on Saturday July 2 between 11:30-1pm.
